  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'Trebuchet MS'\">This Adversary is one whom is an extreme of the natural world. Much like a beast, but so much more. This Adversary cannot be reasoned with making it immune to non jutsu based Social effects or conditions.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Trebuchet MS'\">Additionally, this Adversary deals additional damage to creatures who would have harmed its allies by an amount equal to its level. Once it deals this damage, the bonus damage is no longer applied until it sees the hostile creature harm its allies.</span></p>",
